wiki.summary: This is a release under the moniker of Manes, with the old logo and in the old, slow, depressive black metal style, but not a proper Manes album, as Manes split up officially in 2008. All instruments were recorded by ccernn of (formerly) Manes, and kkoagulaa. The album has only one new track (Solve Et Coagula) the others are re-recordings of old demos. The title track features Kvarforth (Shining) and Malefic (Xasthur) on vocals. Read more on Last.fm.
